title: Rams vs. Seahawks preview; Stafford vs. Wilson; Isaac Bruce; Zack Moss; Swae Lee
itunes:title: Rams vs. Seahawks preview; Stafford vs. Wilson; Isaac Bruce; Zack Moss; Swae Lee
description:
In the latest edition of the Good Morning Football Podcast, hosts Kay Adams, Kyle Brandt, Peter Schrager, and Michael Robinson preview the division rival matchup between the Los Angeles Rams and the Seattle Seahawks! Then they dive into mixed bag trivia where they share stories from Russell Wilson's rookie season; Buffalo Bills running back, Zack Moss, joined the show to discuss the Bills good start to the season; and Hall of Famer, Isaac Bruce joined the show to talk about the Hall of Fame experience and 'The Greatest Show on Turf'

The Good Morning Football Podcast is part of the NFL Podcast Network.
